---
title: Baked Miso & Ginger Chicken with Soy Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: This dish is a perfect combination of bright veggies, miso and ginger-glazed chicken and garlic rice, with the feel-good factor of creating a magnificent Asian-inspired meal from scratch.

